The following scripts are configured be editing /etc/ncid/ncidscript.conf

The ncidscripts.1 man page documents the following scripts.

Script to keep lines in logfile, on Linux, after it is rotated:
    cidrotate

Script to send CID to a cell phone, or pager:
    IMPORTANT: sendmail.cf must hide user root when masquerading is used.
    ncid-page

Script to send CID to samba to get a popup:
    ncid-samba

Script to send CID to a text-to-speach program:
    ncid-speak

Script to display CID on MythTV
    ncid-mythtv

Script to display CID on TiVo
    ncid-tivo
